196
00:16:40,468 --> 00:16:42,034
Sampai bila nak jadi macam tu?

197
00:16:45,185 --> 00:16:48,883
Pakaian seragam itu sesuai dengan anda.

198
00:17:08,094 --> 00:17:09,762
Berapa lama saya akan
hidup seperti ini?

199
00:17:20,212 --> 00:17:22,375
